**Barber** | Townsfolk Killing
__Basics__
Once per game, the Barber may choose to attack one player during the day.
__Details__
After Day 1, the Barber may choose to attack another player. They may only do so once per game.
The Barberâ€™s attack is an end day ability. It is not revealed that the attack was executed by a Barber.

__Simplified__
After Day 1, the Barber may once per game choose to attack one player at the end of the day.

__Formalized__
End Day: Attack @Selection [Temporal: Day 2+, Quantity: 1]

__Card__
The Barber dreams of one day making a big scene and killing that annoying client.
